OL,3,C'I'm just a number to them': Hundreds
OL,4,Cleft out of pocket due to pension
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FITV News Reporter Elaine Willcox spoke
OL,8,Fto Stephen and Julie who retired
OL,9,Fbefore Christmas, but are still
OL,10,Fwaiting for their pension payments.
OL,12,FHundreds of retired government workers
OL,13,Fhave been left waiting for their
OL,14,Fpension payments without an
OL,15,Fexplanation as to why.
OL,17,FStephen Hall and Julie Lawson are
OL,18,Famongst hundreds of former government
OL,19,Fworkers who have been left out of
OL,20,Fpocket due to a backlog of pension
OL,21,Fpayments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
