OL,3,C'I'm just a number to them': Hundreds
OL,4,Cleft out of pocket due to pension
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FStephen was a civil servant for 39
OL,8,Fyears, spending 20 of those in
OL,9,FLiverpool, before he retired in
OL,10,FDecember 2025.
OL,12,FBut now that the government has
OL,13,Foutsourced its pensions scheme to
OL,14,FCapita for the second time, he is one
OL,15,Fof hundreds who are still waiting for
OL,16,Fany pension payment.
OL,18,FHe said: "Imagine after such a good
OL,19,Fcareer, a happy career with HMRC
OL,20,Fworking with such lovely people, it
OL,21,Fleaves a bitter taste in your mouth."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
