OL,3,C'I'm just a number to them': Hundreds
OL,4,Cleft out of pocket due to pension
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,F"I feel like I'm just a number to
OL,8,Fthem, I'm shocked. Imagine you're
OL,9,Fdoing work and you aren't getting
OL,10,Fpaid; it's a similar thing. I've
OL,11,Fworked for 39 years and this is how
OL,12,FI'm treated. I think frankly it's
OL,13,Fdisgusting."
OL,15,FCapita took over the Civil Service
OL,16,FPension Scheme in December 2025 -
OL,17,Ftaking over from previous
OL,18,Fadministrator MyCSP, after a two year
OL,19,Ftransition period. The Cabinet Office
OL,20,Foutsourced the pension scheme to MyCSP
OL,21,Fover 10 years ago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
