OL,3,C'I'm just a number to them': Hundreds
OL,4,Cleft out of pocket due to pension
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FThe company has faced scrutiny for
OL,8,Finheriting a backlog of 86,000 cases,
OL,9,Fand a report by parliament's public
OL,10,Faccounts committee questioned whether
OL,11,FCapita was ready to take over the #239
OL,12,Fmillion contract.
OL,14,FRetired Civil Servant Julie Lawson
OL,15,Fworked in tax for 22 years, but is
OL,16,Falso still waiting for her lump sum
OL,17,Fand pension payments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
