OL,3,C'I'm just a number to them': Hundreds
OL,4,Cleft out of pocket due to pension
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FShe said: "I rang for four or five
OL,8,Fdays solid, and when I finally got
OL,9,Fthrough to them, there was a hundred
OL,10,Fpeople in the queue.
OL,12,FIn a plea to the government, Julie
OL,13,Fsaid: "Please sort it out. We have
OL,14,Fworked hard all our lives for that
OL,15,Fpension, We've paid into it, we've
OL,16,Fworked for you and with you. And the
OL,17,Fleast you can do is get it sorted out
OL,18,Fand paid."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
