OL,3,C'I'm just a number to them': Hundreds
OL,4,Cleft out of pocket due to pension
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FSince taking over the contract, Capita
OL,8,Fsays it has increased staffing to over
OL,9,F500 people to clear the backlog, and
OL,10,Fthe company reports it plans to
OL,11,Fintroduce digital innovation and
OL,12,Fgenerative AI to transform the pension
OL,13,Fexperience for members.
OL,15,FCapita also manages pensions for
OL,16,Fvarious public sector institutions
OL,17,Fincluding HMRC, the MoD and the
OL,18,FScottish government.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
