OL,3,C'I'm just a number to them': Hundreds
OL,4,Cleft out of pocket due to pension
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FA joint statement by Civil Service
OL,8,FChief Operating Officer, Catherine
OL,9,FLittle CB, and Adolfo Hernandez,
OL,10,FCapita CEO said: "When Capita took
OL,11,Fover administration on 1 December 2025
OL,12,Fthey inherited a backlog of 86,000
OL,13,Fcases from the previous administrator,
OL,14,Fa significant proportion of which was
OL,15,Falready overdue. This led to higher
OL,16,Fthan expected volumes of calls and
OL,17,Fcomplex queries which created further
OL,18,Fissues.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
