OL,3,C'I'm just a number to them': Hundreds
OL,4,Cleft out of pocket due to pension
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,F"This is not the service members
OL,8,Fdeserve. Capita and the Cabinet Office
OL,9,Fare deeply sorry for the worry,
OL,10,Ffrustration and distress this has
OL,11,Fcaused - particularly for those
OL,12,Fdealing with bereavement or ill
OL,13,Fhealth."
OL,15,FThe statement said the Cabinet Office
OL,16,Fhas asked Deputy Chief Executive at
OL,17,FHMRC, Angela MacDonald, to lead an
OL,18,Furgent recovery plan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
