OL,3,C'I'm just a number to them': Hundreds
OL,4,Cleft out of pocket due to pension
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FCapita said it is prioritising urgent
OL,8,Fcases such as bereavements, ill health
OL,9,Fand hardship situations, and has took
OL,10,Fon more staff to support in clearing
OL,11,Fthe backlog.
OL,13,FIt said: "Capita expects to restore
OL,14,Fservice levels for the most urgent
OL,15,Fcases by the end of February, with
OL,16,Ffull recovery of the remaining
OL,17,Fpriority cases to follow.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
