OL,3,C'I'm just a number to them': Hundreds
OL,4,Cleft out of pocket due to pension
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,F"In addition to this ongoing activity,
OL,8,FCapita is undertaking a distinct
OL,9,Fproject to complete the outstanding
OL,10,Fwork mandated by the McCloud
OL,11,Fjudgement. This involves issuing
OL,12,Fbenefit choices to approximately
OL,13,F74,000 pensioners and 21,000 deferred
OL,14,Fmembers.
OL,16,F"Both Capita and the Cabinet Office
OL,17,Ftake this responsibility very
OL,18,Fseriously and are urgently working
OL,19,Ftogether to put this right. Further
OL,20,Fupdates will be provided as progress
OL,21,Fis made."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
